    A class to represent a surface as the weighted sum of Zernike polynomials

    Parameters
    ----------
    max_n : int
        The largest of the radial orders
    a : ndarray, optional
        The Zernike polynomial coefficients as a N_SURFxn_modes array; default to all 0
    N_SURF : int, optional
