\subsubsection{Reflection}
\label{sec:reflection}

In the case of reflection, one have $\mu=1$, $b=0$ and
\begin{equation}
  \label{eq:24}
  \Gamma = -2a.
\end{equation}
Eq.~(\ref{eq:14}) thus becomes
\begin{equation}
  \label{eq:25}
    \vec \Sp = \vec S -2a \vec r.
\end{equation}
